0.text: Tibeddit tecreḍ daɣen azemz n uzref n umeckuk n weẓmaẓ arurad.

1.text: Ass-agi zik, aḍu yella tamudi n 83km/h, yerna urǧan-t ad ikemmel ad yettenkar.

2.text: Agman agejdan n unagraw uwnis d ul, i d tassufut n idamen.

3.text: Isemla web-agi fkan-asen aṭas n wazal, abaɛda deg yimukan n leqraya.

4.text: Ddurat rxisent kter i yigrawen imeqqranen, s wakka ma uḥdek i telliḍ neɣ akked yiwen kan n umdakkel, ɛṛeḍ ad d-waliḍ imdanen niḍen xedmet agraw n ukkuz ar seddis iwakken ad ilhu i yal yiwen.

5.text: Kra n tweṣṣafin n isura n imusal ilemmusa sexdament amasal n 6 ɣef 6 cm, s wudem usdid ibbaw n 56 ɣef 56 mm.

6.text: Xdem-d yarna awi talsuffɣin n tsertit-ik akked isallen yaɛnan ṭamen-ik akkid-k.

7.text: Aččaṛ axxam-ik s lqahwa tanesbaɣuṛt sbeḥ akked ciṭ n latay n kamumi id-ittawin astaɛfu deg yiḍ.

8.text: Adfel i d-yettegririben seg yidurar ur yelli d waramagnu; tikessarin yettecgen zemrent kan ad ṭṭfent ciṭ n umurḍes, yerna taččart n waṭas ad ɣlin d agrireb.

9.text: Taẓeṭṭaṭ n yedrimen i tettaɣeḍ tebna s umgarad deg tmura yemgaraden, yerna ifmiḍiyen d wazalen n tẓeṭṭaṭ d anḍiyen mliḥ si tmurt ɣer tayeḍ.

7.text: Aččaṛ axxam-ik s lqahwa tanesbaɣuṛt sbeḥ akked ciṭ n latay n kamumi id-ittawin astaɛfu deg yiḍ.

8.text: Adfel i d-yettegririben seg yidurar ur yelli d waramagnu; tikessarin yettecgen zemrent kan ad ṭṭfent ciṭ n umurḍes, yerna taččart n waṭas ad ɣlin d agrireb.
